{"tid":1667991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈，咪錶擊敗交通燈成為今次運動倖存者","createTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T19:31:36.000Z","uid":262063,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4324b11af36cba92b0cbe46d07b0b9d23ba7c641","tid":1667991,"uid":262063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"6月至今，香港18區已近全部食過tg又開過花<br />\n交通燈拆嘅拆，黑店裝修嘅裝修<br />\n大家為左cut政府同黨鉄收入<br />\n交税要分千次<br />\n八達通都cut埋，都係希望政府收入減少一蚊得一蚊<br />\n<br />\n但行來行去經過見到好多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直接為政府帶來收入嘅咪錶居然完好無缺！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真心希望咪錶可以咁樣繼續運作<br />\n證明大家抗爭之中不忘守法泊車<br />\n唔好講到打爛，只係簡單噴黑睇唔到紅燈有無閃<br />\n又看不到mon，都已經唔知點入錢或入左多錢<br />\n<br />\n查一查<br />\n2018年政府咪錶收入2.87億元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔好睇少十元八塊<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為而家無人得閒炒牌<br />\n問下有車人士<br />\n就會發現有關部門仲係好努力工作<br />\n<br />\n藍絲咁守法，泊低架車發現入唔到錶，肯定會心痛咪錶機壞左，泊車都被迫要犯法，分分鐘心臟病發添<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以千祈唔好搞咪錶！！可大可小！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另，原來好多人唔知點搵咪錶位<br />\n雖然好多咪錶都喺內街<br />\n不過唔使怕，政府網站有晒list<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/parking/parking_meters/octopus_operated_parking_meters/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftransport_in_hong_kong%2Fparking%2Fparking_meters%2Foctopus_operated_parking_meters%2Findex.html&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=12d7e6ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/parking/parking_meters/octopus_operated_parking_meters/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n祝各位有車人士路上平安<br />\n合法入錶泊車，咪俾人炒牌"},{"pid":"fc78b5d433415c9a67671e5977d157fd58603be2","tid":1667991,"uid":298061,"like":0,"d